
To install MySQL Workbench, follow these steps:

For Windows:
Download MySQL Workbench:

Go to the https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/windows/installer/8.0.html
Choose your Windows version and download the installer.
Run the Installer:

Once the download is complete, run the installer.
Follow the prompts in the setup wizard. You may need to choose whether to install MySQL Workbench as a standalone application or as part of a larger MySQL installation.
Complete Installation:

The installer will guide you through the installation process. Make sure to review and confirm the installation settings.
Launch MySQL Workbench:

After installation, you can find MySQL Workbench in your Start Menu. Open it and configure your database connections.
